      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 2.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.066666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、どうしたんだ？\nリハーサルでも調子がよくなさそうだったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ what’s the matter?\nYou didn’t seem in top form during rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.4333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……実は、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}… To be honest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも言ってくれ\n本番前に気になることは解決しておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Go ahead. You can tell me anything.\nLet’s resolve this before the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 18.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今更なんですけど……\nやっぱりこんな格好で人前に出るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know it’s a bit late for this…\nBut going out in front of people‚ dressed like this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "も、もの凄く、恥ずかしいというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "i-is actually really embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.433333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "歌も動きもキレがなかったのはそれが原因か\n気恥ずかしい気持ちは分からないでもないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That explains the hesitancy in your singing and dancing.\nI can understand where you’re coming from‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーである琴乃がそんな風だと\nみんなもいつもの力を発揮出来なくなってしまうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you’re the leader‚ Kotono.\nThe others need you to set an example.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、私のせいで月ストのみんなに\n迷惑はかけられないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I don’t want to cause any trouble\nfor the other members of Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 47.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、この衣装だとちょっと、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which is exactly why‚ this costume‚ it’s a bit—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "衣装は前に確認したし、試着もしただろ？\nあの時はなんともなかったじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You had a fitting and everything‚ right?\nYou didn’t say anything then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それも分かってます\n分かってるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I know I didn’t.\nI know‚ but still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "昨日までは本番に向けてとにかく必死で\n気にする余裕がなかったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was desperate just to reach this point.\nI didn’t have time to worry about it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 69.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、本番直前になって、改めて冷静に見てみたら……\nな、なんだか露出が多くありませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But right before the concert‚ I took another look…\nand I think it shows off a bit too much skin?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 81.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "発注したのは{user}さんですよね？\nその辺りは気にならなかったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the one who ordered them‚ right?\nDidn’t you think about that stuff?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 86.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "リハーサルの時も全身で風を感じてる気がして……\n涼しいはずなのに身体が熱くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could feel the wind everywhere on my body during rehearsals…\nbut I felt hot‚ not cold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "よくよく考えたら、水着風衣装って言っても\n水着と変わらないじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about it‚ “swimwear style”\nis just another way of saying “swimwear!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 100.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私、これから水着でお客さんの前に……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m about to go in front of the audience in a bikini!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I pull this off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、落ち着いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ calm down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ\nすみません、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah!\nI’m sorry. I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 113.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと頭を冷やしてきます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to cool off a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 116.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃダメだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t leave her like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
