    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 119.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nもう、わざわざ追いかけて来たんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nYou came after me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 126.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "急に飛び出して行ったら、放っておけないだろ\nそれに、きちんと伝えておきたくてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You kinda rushed off. I was worried.\nAnd there’s something I wanted to say.",
